---
title: Mushroom Panzanella Salad with Mozzarella and Caramelised Onion
description: Mimi admits that salad isn’t her favourite thing - but her mushroom panzanella salad with mozzarella and caramelised onion is ‘something else’. For a salad with bells on - get panzanella-ing!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/572322dbfd2cb93c648b4567.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/572322dbfd2cb93c648b4567.pdf
author: HelloFresh
nutrition:
  calories: 365 kcal
  fat: 14 g
  saturated fat: 10 g
  carbohydrates: 32 g
  protein: 20 g
course: main course
